data.description: Rare Family find close to Everything! Situated between Jacksonville, Medford and Central Point sits this 5+ acre rural jewel. Located in the coveted Jacksonville school district this property is one to see. Located well off the road with private driveway you will find this fully fenced property with 1225 sqft farmhouse, 1500 sq.ft. 4 bay metal shop, huge garden areas with water, and views of the surrounding hills. The home itself is a very well taken care of modest home with 2 bed, 2 bath, large living area/kitchen, and dedicated laundry room. Tons of parking with RV hookups, separate garden areas, excellent domestic well and plenty of room to make this your own! Don't miss this one.
